ogirihighschool.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">青雾高中</a>”的<a href="https://x.com/harusame_urame" target="_blank" rel="noopener">春雨丽</a>被任命为“Puyo Puyo eSports”的官方大使。</p><p>今后，双方将以“全国县电子竞技2024 SAGA Puyo Puyo分区”为中心，合作搞活“Puyo Puyo”锦标赛。还计划在现场直播和锦标赛新颖方面进行合作。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="【#重要公告】今天好像有一个非常重要的公告！ [#春雨丽城#青桐高中]" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/3a043Rfl4VQ?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> （参考）<a href="https://prtimes.jp/main/html/rd/p/000005900.000005397.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">世嘉株式会社新闻稿</a></p><h2>涩谷春红牛特别合作活动即将举办</h2><p><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/08/641139fd86c01c72545aab9222f5a942-kix.sxalutqklbx-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/08/641139fd86c01c72545aab9222f5a942-kix.sxalutqklbx-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 339px) 100vw, 339px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/08/641139fd86c01c72545aab9222f5a942-kix.sxalutqklbx-jpg.webp 339w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/08/641139fd86c01c72545aab9222f5a942-kix.sxalutqklbx-212x300.webp 212w" width="339" height="480" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://twitter.com/shibuyahal" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Haru Shibuya</a>和 Red Bull 的特别合作活动<span style="background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255);">将于 8 月 11 日（星期日）在埼玉、千叶和东京的 34 家罗森商店（不包括“Natural Lawson”和“Lawson Store 100”）举行。</span></p><p><span style="background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255);">为了纪念这次合作，我们将推出限量版红牛 3 罐套装。标准版附有模切贴纸，国际天空城站前店特别版附有A6贴纸。</span></p><p><span style="background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255);">贴纸背面附有二维码，可让您欣赏 Haru Shibuya 在工作时收听的推荐动漫歌曲播放列表。</span></p><p> （参考）<a href="https://prtimes.jp/main/html/rd/p/000000143.000049143.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Red Bull Japan Co., Ltd.新闻稿</a></p><h2>“